      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "THINKING OF YOU (2) goes very well at this journey here having never missed the frame including six wins. Scored by 4 lengths last time (19.51) in a Other over 342m at this track. Looks the one to beat with even luck. RHINESTONE (1) made light work of the tricky draw with a strong early sectional but swamped late when a close up fifth (31.34) at this track over 530m. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Should be in this for a long way. INDIE OR JILL (3) turned in a modest effort most recently when fifth at Gawler over 400m behind Binnaway Warrior (23.10) in a Grade 4/5. Likely to play a prominent role. TOORA TERRY (8) is another with top-three prospects.",
